reviews.text: Friendly staffs and serve great food, the Hokkien mee is highly recommended, wok hey and pork lard that elevate the taste. Must go with their in-house chilli. They have pretty good live band too. They sang mostly nostalgic songs but still it‚Äôs nice and chill. Will come back again.
The sound system is awesome! The karaoke system really good w big screen. Friendly service staff. Cosy and friendly chill out place.

Chill place to come for drinks and friends catch up! Highly recommend the Balvenie 12 years promotion. Smooth whisky and there is karaoke session tonight! 2 songs per table and I like the projections on the wall for my song ü§ó

The female waitress service is really sweet and prompt. Check out this place soon!

The Hokkien Mee is superb! They really take serious about the foods taste, with crunchy pork lard, generous portion with big prawns, scallops and lots of gravy. The boss say the chillies is homemade with special recipe. Must come to try this. So much better than all famous Hokkien Mee outside !

Best choice to chill out with yummilicious food and impeccable service especially from Danny and Roger. The special of the day-  seafood lala beehoon was infused with great umami flavour. Beer bites were perfectly served and non oily. Ambience was cosy... with sakura and beautiful positive vibes.
